de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcore.controlnodes

Class XorGatewayInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcore.controlnodes.AbstractControlNodeInstance
      • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcore.controlnodes.GatewayInstance
        • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcore.controlnodes.XorGatewayInstance

  • public class XorGatewayInstance
extends GatewayInstance
    Represents exclusive gateways. In contrast to the BPMN specification, exclusive gateways are handled like event based gateways. All following control nodes are enabled, and skipped when one of them begins.
